location.fullValue: Abbeyville Plan, Del Webb at Lake Oconee

data.description: Rare find - three bedroom/2bath home on .68 acre lot in Greene County (Charter school district) with full basement.  Large master bedroom on the main, vaulted trey ceilings, separate dining room, laundry room, garden tub, split bedroom plan, double vanity, walk in closet.  Neighborhood has community dock.  Recent updates - exterior painted, decks refinished and painted, HVAC replaced in 2019, garage floor painted with special finish.  Unfinished walkout basement has some drywall providing potential for additional living space.  Home is conveniently located in the desirable Eagle View subdivision just minutes from Lake Oconee and easy access to Interstate 20.
